{"id": "1443860573740601515", "channel_id": "1443860573740601515", "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "content": "食堂专座上无人分享的小蛋糕，建校人雕像旁孤单萌芽的树苗，笛音空旷回荡的音乐教室。\n\n校园的每一个角落，好像都缺了点什么。\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nA single, small cake rests forgotten on a reserved cafeteria chair.\n\nBy the Principal's statue, a solitary sapling pushes up from the earth. \n\nThe notes of a flute ring hollowly through the empty music room.\n\nAn air of incompleteness permeates every corner of the campus.", "timestamp": "2025-11-28T07:06:26.412000+00:00", "thread_id": "1443860573740601515", "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1400771650064089112", "count": 50}, {"emoji": "M_satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 15}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1443860574936109118", "filename": "003-1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 11821157, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1443860573740601515/1443860574936109118/003-1.jpg?ex=69ccc3f2&is=69cb7272&hm=043ee3566bf745ff64cf521de6cc4d9637b68fc84cfb1ca9c9d4e3adfb25b5ce&"}, {"id": "1443860575728701490", "filename": "003-2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 6086730, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1443860573740601515/1443860575728701490/003-2.jpg?ex=69ccc3f2&is=69cb7272&hm=df69d24f1c46d5667266b83d3927171e1dbf9d3f5fd9cf2b40751adf35f15c45&"}]}
